author: Martha D
title: Great place to stay prior to sfo departures
text: This beautiful well maintained old hotel is so well organized. Restaurant is good. Our suite had kitchen with all needed supplies. Staff very pleasant. Park stay fly program well organized. Will stay in future again when flying out of SFO.
